        "gg1Z04GcUw4_text": "<p>Caleb</p>",
        "gg7q2O1ZmZZ_text": "<p>The differences are just awesome. I feel brighter, like my head is clearer and overall, I feel more like myself again. I feel like I was the kid I was when I was 7–8, just full of energy—honestly, it’s amazing!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggLEM4N6KwF_text": "<p>Hector&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggLs2jDS76d_text": "<p>Just wanted to say thank you for making this mouthguard, I had a exam today and I had to cram until 4am and only slept three hours. I was able to get through the entire day without feeling as tired. Thank you so much for making this mouthguard.</p>",
        "ggUI_Pq11fn_text": "<p>Ben</p>"
      }
    },
